      <title>南非将于本财年设立气候应对基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/south-africa-to-establish-climate-response-fund-this-fiscal-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非环境部长迪翁乔治表示，南非预计将于本财年（3月31日结束）设立气候变化应对基金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/south-africa-to-establish-climate-response-fund-this-fiscal-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 14:56:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
